  "customHelp": "How to play Alpha Clash TCG:\n- Each player starts with a Contender (your main character with health points).\n- Draw 8 cards to start. You may mulligan once.\n- First player skips their draw phase on turn 1.\n- Each turn: Untap → Draw → Resource (play 1 card face-down) → Main → Clash → Main 2 → End.\n- Tap resources to pay for cards. Any card can be a resource.\n- Attack your opponent's Contender or their Clash cards.\n- Reduce opponent's Contender health to 0 to win!\n\nZones: Oblivion = graveyard, Banished = exiled cards.",
